#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/basics.rst:26
msgid ""
"Pressing :kbd:`G` activates \"Grab/Move\" transformation mode. The "
"selected object or element then moves freely according to the mouse "
"pointer's location and camera."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/editors/3dview/object/editing/transform/basics.rst:29
